BACKGROUND.Journey with SMA: Michelle was diagnosed with SMA at the age of three, initially misdiagnosed with Weierman Costman Syndrome, which was later corrected to SMA Type 3. She walked until she was 12 or 13 and transitioned to a wheelchair in late middle school. Over the years, she has experienced a decline in strength and abilities, particularly in the last ten to fifteen years, but remains active and ambitious.
BACKGROUND.Current Health Description: Michelle describes her current health as stable but acknowledges a decline in strength over the past decade.
